llection, use and distribution of         the information.\n\tWhat types of security procedures are in place to protect the loss, misuse or         alteration of\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Information under Media Design Group Inc. control.\n\tHow users can correct any inaccuracies in the information.\n\n\n\n\nIf users have questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, they should first contact Media Design Group Inc., Customer Support Department at webmaster@enviousescorts.com or Tel: (415) 553-8069 / Fax: (415) 558-8069                                                                       \n\n\n\nInformation Collection and Use\n\n\n\nMedia Design Group Inc. is the sole owner of the information collected on all websites owned and operated by Media Design Group Inc. In addition, Media Design Group Inc. may collect information from our users at several different points on our web sites.\n\n\u00a0\n\nRegistration\n\n\n\nIn order to use one of the above Web sites, a user may first be required to complete a registration form. During registration a user may be required to give contact information (such as name and email address). We may use this information to contact the user about services on our site for which he/she has expressed interest. It may be optional for the user to provide demographic information (such as income level and gender) and unique identifiers (such as, username and password) but encouraged so we can provide a more personalized experience on our site.\n\n\n\nMedia Design Group Inc. Order\n\n\n\nWe may request information from the user on our order or registration form. A user may be requested to provide contact information (such as name, email, and shipping address) and financial information (such as credit card number, expiration date). This information may be used for billing purposes and to fill customer\u2019s orders. If we have trouble processing an order, the information may be used to contact the user.\n