d a newsletter. Out of respect for the privacy of our users we may present the option to not receive these types of communications. Please see the Choice and Opt-out sections.\n\n\n\nEnvious Entertainment Newsletter\n\n\n\nIf a user wishes to subscribe to our Envious Entertainment newsletter, we may ask for contact information such as name and email address. Out of respect for our users privacy we may provide a way to opt-out of these communications.\n\n\n\nMedia Design Group Inc. Service Announcements\n\nOn rare occasions it may be necessary to send out a strictly service related announcement. For instance, if our service is temporarily suspended we might send users an email. Generally, users may not opt-out of these communications, though they may be able to deactivate their account. However, these communications may not be promotional in nature.\n\n\n\nMedia Design Group Inc. Customer Service\n\n\n\nWe may communicate with users on a regular basis to provide requested services and in regards to issues relating to their account we may reply via email or phone, in accordance with the user\u2019s wishes.\n\n\n\nMedia Design Group Inc. Legal Disclaimer\n\n\n\nThough we make every effort to preserve user privacy, we may need to disclose personal information when required by law wherein we have a good-faith belief that such action is necessary to comply with a current judicial proceeding, a court order or legal process served on our Web sites.\n\n\n\nWe DO NOT Share Personal Information with Third Parties\n\n\n\nThird Party Intermediaries\n\n\n\nWe may use an outside shipping company to ship orders and a credit card processing company to bill users for goods and services. These companies do not retain, share, store or use personally identifiable information for any secondary purposes.\n\n\n\nMedia Design Group Inc. Service Providers\n\n\n\nWe may from time to time partner with other third parties to provide specific services. When the user signs up for these particular